Entries.default: "I don't know how we're breathing, but I'm not complaining. Ishi, don't go far."
"At least I don't need to hold my breath, but something about that pool makes me want to."
"The air down here may be breathable, but that doesn't make it sanitary."
"It's great that they got air down here somehow. But I wouldn't mind if it smelled like something besides rotten fish."
"I have read that the inventor Iverra has experimented with devices to bring air under water, but this appears to be something on a far grander scale."
"If I done told Remaro there were air underwater once, I told him a hundred times. That old salt be owing me a suole."
"I'm glad I'm not drowning, but I got to admit, breathing under water makes my head hurt."
